'''劣生学'''是研究特定人口或物种中，后代缺陷或不利基因累积和保存的学科。 劣生突变已在例如老鼠<ref>{{cite journal|author = Tanabe T, Beam KG, Powell JA, Numa S|title = Restoration of excitation-contraction coupling and slow calcium current in dysgenic muscle by dihydropyridine receptor complementary DNA|journal = Nature|volume = 336|issue = 6195|pages = 134–9|date = November 1988|pmid = 2903448|doi = 10.1038/336134a0|url = http://www.nature.com/nature/journal/v336/n6195/abs/336134a0.html|access-date = 2015-07-09|archive-date = 2016-04-12|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160412233830/http://www.nature.com/nature/journal/v336/n6195/abs/336134a0.html}}</ref> 和果蝇中证明存在<ref>{{cite journal |author = Kidwell MG|title = Evolution of hybrid dysgenesis determinants in Drosophila melanogaster|journal = Proc. Natl. Acad. Sci. U.S.A.|volume = 80|issue = 6|pages = 1655–9|date = March 1983|pmid = 6300863|pmc = 393661|url = http://www.pnas.org/cgi/pmidlookup?view=long&pmid=6300863|doi = 10.1073/pnas.80.6.1655}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|url = http://www.scielo.br/scielo.php?pid=S0073-47212002000200007&script=sci_arttext&tlng=|title = Gonadal hybrid dysgenesis in ''Drosophila Sturtevanti'' (Diptera, Drosophilidae)|journal = Iheringia, Sér. Zool.|volume = 92|issue = 2|date = June 2002|doi = 10.1590/S0073-47212002000200007|author = Almeida LM, Carareto CMA|access-date = 2015-07-09|archive-date = 2019-06-08|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190608112644/http://www.scielo.br/scielo.php?pid=S0073-47212002000200007&script=sci_arttext&tlng=}}</ref>。英文''dysgenics'' 最初作为优生学（eugenics）的反义词而使用。Richard Lynn 博士在Dysgenics：遺傳惡化在現代人群（1996）確定了三個主要的擔憂：人類族群中健康，智力以及責任心的喪失。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bartleby.com/61/60/D0446000.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2009-01-25 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090318135516/http://www.bartleby.com/61/60/D0446000.html |archivedate=2009-03-18 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://medical.merriam-webster.com/medical/dysgenics |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2009-01-25 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120720150508/http://medical.merriam-webster.com/medical/dysgenics |archivedate=2012-07-20 }}</ref>

== 原因 ==
任何生物的基因都会产生突变，这种突变是多害少利的。自然中，更不适应的个体被淘汰，更适应的个体得以产生更多后代，于是有害突变倾向于被清除，有利突变倾向于扩散。

人口退化有两种解释：工业革命后一般智力因素较低的人群更高的生育率；原本自然选择会筛选掉有害突变，而现代人口中这种选择力量降低。 <ref>of Menie, Michael A. Woodley. </ref><ref name="lynn">{{cite journal|title=Dysgenic fertility for criminal behaviour|journal=Journal of Biosocial Science|doi=10.1017/s0021932000023014|url=https://www.cambridge.org/core/journals/journal-of-biosocial-science/article/dysgenic-fertility-for-criminal-behaviour/6CF6E3CFF6BAFE3EBD497746E7236162|date=1995/10|volume=27|issue=4|pages=405–408|issn=1469-7599|language=en|accessdate=2018-04-02|author=Richard Lynn|archive-date=2020-06-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200615163703/https://www.cambridge.org/core/journals/journal-of-biosocial-science/article/dysgenic-fertility-for-criminal-behaviour/6CF6E3CFF6BAFE3EBD497746E7236162}}</ref>

== 智商退化 ==
2004年，Richard Lynn的研究認為在美國社會每經過一個世代就有0.9分智商下降。<ref>{{Cite journal | last1 = Lynn | first1 = R | title = New evidence of dysgenic fertility for intelligence in the United States | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_intelligence_2004_32_2/page/193 | doi = 10.1016/j.intell.2003.09.002 | journal = Intelligence | volume = 32 | issue = 2 | pages = 193–201 | year = 2004 | pmid =  | pmc = }}</ref>

Meisenberg（2010）發現，在美國雙親的智力和兒童的數量呈負相關，通常那些智力跟受教育程度更高，思想越自由的人生育率就越低，在沒有引進移民的狀態下美國人的智商每隔一代就會下降大約0.8分。<ref>{{Cite journal | last1 = Meisenberg | first1 = Gerhard | title = The reproduction of intelligence | doi = 10.1016/j.intell.2010.01.003 | journal = Intelligence | volume = 38 | issue = 2 | pages = 220–230 | year = 2010 | pmid =  | pmc = }}</ref>

== 其他性状的的退化 ==
1996年Lynn出版了专著''Dysgenics: Genetic Deterioration in Modern Populations。''他指出了优生学家的三大考虑：健康、智商、公德心的降低。他认为，工业化前的社会中自然选择倾向选择的一些性状，比如高智商，在现今社会已经不再那样。<ref name="lynn">{{cite journal|title=Dysgenic fertility for criminal behaviour|journal=Journal of Biosocial Science|doi=10.1017/s0021932000023014|url=https://www.cambridge.org/core/journals/journal-of-biosocial-science/article/dysgenic-fertility-for-criminal-behaviour/6CF6E3CFF6BAFE3EBD497746E7236162|date=1995/10|volume=27|issue=4|pages=405–408|issn=1469-7599|language=en|accessdate=2018-04-02|author=Richard Lynn}}</ref>

英文中，“优生学”第一次在1915年由David Starr Jordan作为形容词使用，形容第一次世界大战中的效应<ref>''[[牛津英語詞典|Oxford English Dictionary]]''</ref>。他认为，在现代战争中由于健康的男子比别人更容易死掉，战争只会杀掉平民中的健康男子，却保存残疾人在家。<ref name="Jordan">{{cite book|last = Jordan|first = David Starr|title = War and the Breed: The Relation of War to the Downfall of Nations|publisher = University Press of the Pacific|year = 2003|edition = Reprint|isbn = 1-4102-0900-8|location = Honolulu, Hawaii}}</ref>

== 基因缺陷 ==
随着医学的发展和社保的提高，基因缺陷的概率也随着上升。此问题可以通过基因咨询或者产前筛查减轻。<ref>{{cite journal|title=Effects of various medical and social pracitices on the frequency of genetic disorders|pages=614–627|issn=0002-9297|journal=American Journal of Human Genetics|volume=27|issue=5|date=1975-9|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/1163536|accessdate=2019-05-25|author=S. M. Holloway, C. Smith|pmid=1163536|pmc=PMC1762830|archive-date=2019-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190612135919/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/1163536}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|url=http://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/0165111083900404|pages=449–457|title=Perspectives in mutation epidemiology: 5. Modern medical practice versus environmental mutagens: Their possible dysgenic impact|journal=Mutation Research/Reviews in Genetic Toxicology|volume=114|issue=3|accessdate=2018-04-02|doi=10.1016/0165-1110(83)90040-4|author=E. Matsunaga|archive-date=2019-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190612053127/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/0165111083900404}}</ref>

== 其他解决方法 ==
对于人口退化问题的解决，Lynn and Harvey (2008)认为设计婴儿可以在未来有很大的前途。如果有的国家禁止设计婴儿，有钱人会先出国实施，逐渐更多人也会跟随。另外，权威政体可能会通过只允许一定智商之上的人生育。中国的计划生育政策就证明了，权威政体可以控制生育。<ref name="ReferenceB">{{cite journal|url=http://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0160289607000463|pages=112–120|title=The decline of the world's IQ|journal=Intelligence|volume=36|issue=2|accessdate=2018-04-02|doi=10.1016/j.intell.2007.03.004|author=Richard Lynn, John Harvey|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308062801/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0160289607000463}}</ref>  Geoffrey Miller宣称，用于对抗人口大幅增长的计划生育政策也有利于“降低边缘农民的劣生效应”。<ref>Edge, Chinese Eugenics, http://edge.org/response-detail/23838/ {{Wayback|url=http://edge.org/response-detail/23838/ |date=20140901060742 }}</ref> 然而现实是，一胎政策长期都允许农民生两个孩子。

== 小说中的描写 ==
Cyril M. Kornbluth1951年出版的小说''The Marching Morons''中，不小心来到未来的两个人，发现人口退化导致人们很笨。 Mike Judge 2006年电影''Idiocracy'' （译名《蠢蛋进化论》）也讲了类似的情节，主角是参加军队冬眠实验计划主角，他到达了500年后，由于高智商的知识分子生育率低，受教育程度低的人生育率高，导致人类智商降低。 Kornbluth的短故事中，文明由一小组天才维持，而在电影''Idiocracy''中是由自动系统持续。<ref>{{cite news|url = http://www.nytimes.com/2006/09/09/business/09online.html|title = Shying away from Degeneracy|work = The New York Times|author = Mitchell, Dan|date = 2006-09-09|accessdate = 2008-06-29|archive-date = 2022-05-22|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220522220109/https://www.nytimes.com/2006/09/09/business/09online.html}}</ref>

